caption:
【FRI-13-MAR] ↓ info ↓
/// DORIAN PAIC - Few figures capture Frankfurt’s house and techno heritage like Dorian Paic. From the jet-set disco Dorian Gray and Sven Väth’s Omen to cult spaces like XS, Monza, and Robert Johnson, he’s been a constant presence shaping the city’s rhythm. A longtime force behind Freebase Records and head of the influential label raum…musik, Paic’s deep, hypnotic sound has carried him from intimate floors to Love Family Park, Cocoon nights, and beyond. Always rooted in groove and precision, he remains a cornerstone of the German underground, a DJ’s DJ who plays for those who truly listen.

/// ANDI CAZ - Cornerstone of Porto’s underground scene, known for his deep connection to the dancefloor and his sharp sense of groove. A long-time resident at the legendary Lottus after-hours, he’s perfected the craft of late-night storytelling through sound. Beyond the booth, he runs HomeMade Records and curates nights under the Hypnosis banner, blending his role as DJ, label head, and promoter. With over a decade of releases supported by key players across the scene, Andy Caz continues to shape Porto’s sonic landscape, always authentic, always forward-thinking.

/// DA NI - Selector shaped by the dance floor, blending deep house grooves with raw, unconventional shades of techno. A founding force behind Propaganda 085 alongside Nuno di Rosso and Wailers, he’s carved a path through Portugal’s underground scene with a rebellious spirit. Known for his deep vinyl digging, Da Ni curates rare 90s gems and forgotten tracks that capture the pulse of the era. Behind the decks, his sets unfold like stories — crafted from texture, tension, and timeless rhythm.

━☆ ＲŪＭＵ ☆━
ᴇᴀᴛ, ᴅʀɪɴᴋ ɴ’ ᴅᴀɴᴄᴇ - ʀᴜᴀ ɴᴏᴠᴀ ᴅᴀ  ᴛʀɪɴᴅᴀᴅᴇ 5ɢ ʟɪꜱʙᴏɴ - ᴠɪꜱɪᴛ ᴏᴜʀ ᴡᴇʙꜱɪᴛᴇ - ɴᴏ ᴘʜᴏɴᴇꜱ ᴏɴ ᴛʜᴇ ᴅᴀɴᴄᴇꜰʟᴏᴏʀ - ʀᴇꜱᴘᴇᴄᴛ ᴛʜᴇ ꜱᴘᴀᴄᴇ ᴀɴᴅ ᴇᴀᴄʜ ᴏᴛʜᴇʀ.

